        <section eId="sec_17a_814">
          <num>17a-814</num>
          <heading>(Formerly Sec. 10-297). Employment and aid</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 17a-814. (Formerly Sec. 10-297). Employment and aid.The Commissioner of Aging and Disability Services is authorized to aid in securing employment for persons who are legally blind. Said commissioner may aid persons who are legally blind in such way as said commissioner deems expedient, expending for such purpose such sum as the General Assembly appropriates.
